  "title": "Dietetic Technician (5 days Office hour) - Up to 3K #HHL",
  "description": "<p>💰 Salary: $2,500 – $3,000</p><p>⏰Working Hours: Mon - Fri, 8.30am - 6pm</p><p>📍Queenstown</p><p></p><p>🌟 Job Scope</p><ul><li>Support Dietitians and Manager in administrative and nutrition-related tasks</li><li>Assist in preparing nutrition education materials, slides, and programmes</li><li>Handle patient appointment booking, reminders, and basic pre-clerking</li><li>Perform nutritional analysis using computer software</li><li>Manage oral nutrition supplement (ONS) samples and ensure proper tracking</li><li>Update department website, records, and reports</li><li>Assist with data entry, statistics, and research support</li><li>Answer phone calls and handle general enquiries</li></ul><p>✅ Requirements: Minimum Diploma in Applied Science</p><p></p><p>If interested, please email me at alexgoh@recruitexpress.com.sg or telegram @alexgohhl</p><p>➖</p><p>Alex Goh Hock Leong</p><p>(CEI.No: R1763413 l Recruit Express Pte Ltd (Healthcare & Life Science) | 99C4599)</p>",
